Package: brightnexus
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0, libsecret-1-0
Description: BrightNexus for Linux — TPM2-backed BrightLink bridge
 BrightNexus for Linux is the hardware-anchored BrightLink credential agent
 for Ubuntu and other Linux desktops. It exposes EBP/1 + BrightLink on a
 per-user Unix socket and provides a GTK4 system-tray UI for live credentials.
 .
 This package installs:
  * brightnexus — GTK4 / libadwaita system-tray application
  * brightnexus-bridge — headless bridge binary for servers and CI
 .
 Bridge identity prefers TPM2 when available; set BRIGHTNEXUS_REQUIRE_HARDWARE=1
 to refuse software-only fallback.
